{"tid":1217652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急）我做酒店，大家要知，保護自己","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:48:03.000Z","uid":179882,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f286798912ec48a210b71c3ef61a414d3319816","tid":1217652,"uid":179882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"我以前係做酒店，而家無做，不過仲喺個酒店whatsapp group 入面，個經理係個group 度講：<br />\n<br />\nTuen Mun Pentahotel 發出內部通知叫員工留意懷疑因示威而到酒店住嘅客，如果有懷疑就要通知保安部<br />\n<br />\n通知保安部唔係唔比人入住，而係要記錄曬佢地嘅資料同埋係酒店內嘅一舉一動，日後黑警有需要時就會交出所有相關資料幫黑警入案！<br />\n<br />\n相信唔止一間酒店會咁，所以大家要小心"},{"pid":"6d5ff084c1368346804bc53f3ee12cb39929215a","tid":1217652,"uid":31947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0723478dcfe88adf95af94906955f71c7b2a9aa7","tid":1217652,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:40:43.000Z","msg":"仆街到， push"},{"pid":"176fb55c95c94b119aa4c1e13fc67913fae4f185","tid":1217652,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}